
00:00:01,101 --> 00:00:02,936
Narrator:
Tonight on "Shark Tank,"
Daniel Lubetzky, the founder

00:00:02,936 --> 00:00:05,305
of the groundbreaking
snack company "KIND,"

00:00:05,305 --> 00:00:05,839
returns to the Tank.

00:00:05,839 --> 00:00:07,608
You're one of the most
impressive people

00:00:07,608 --> 00:00:08,942
I've seen in a very long time.

00:00:08,942 --> 00:00:11,678
Marcotte: This tiny object
changed everything.

00:00:11,678 --> 00:00:14,081
Sharks,
let us break the ice.

00:00:14,515 --> 00:00:17,751
Your logo is so close
to Scrub Daddy's.

00:00:17,751 --> 00:00:18,719
I'm doing this alone.

00:00:18,719 --> 00:00:19,853
