00:00:19,853 --> 00:00:22,356
I will never not know
how to make money.

00:00:22,356 --> 00:00:23,557
That doesn't matter!

00:00:23,557 --> 00:00:25,659
I want to buy
the entire company.

00:00:25,659 --> 00:00:27,394
We would take a million.
Bam.

00:00:27,394 --> 00:00:28,495
