00:06:17,611 --> 00:06:18,979
[ Herjavec laughs ]
Okay.

00:06:18,979 --> 00:06:21,481
And ‐‐ Well, I don't hear you
putting up a check.

00:06:21,481 --> 00:06:23,350
[ Laughter ]
Thank you.

00:06:23,350 --> 00:06:24,651
You are a Shark.

00:06:24,651 --> 00:06:26,820
What I don't know is
tomorrow morning,

00:06:26,820 --> 00:06:29,689
vaccine, people get on
with their lives,

00:06:29,689 --> 00:06:30,757
and they're saying,
"What was that puzzle?"

00:06:30,757 --> 00:06:31,958
I mean,
that's the problem.

00:06:31,958 --> 00:06:33,693
I don't ‐‐
Cuban: You know, as crazy
as Mr. Wonderful is,

00:06:33,693 --> 00:06:34,928
he's right in
one respect.

00:06:34,928 --> 00:06:37,864
The problem is
just the valuation.

00:06:37,864 --> 00:06:40,367
You've got to make
$10 million in cash flow

00:06:40,367 --> 00:06:41,434
that you distribute

00:06:41,434 --> 00:06:43,470
in order for that 5% of that

00:06:43,470 --> 00:06:45,772
to come back
as $500,000 to me.

00:06:45,772 --> 00:06:47,641
Look, there are
a lot of great branders.

00:06:47,641 --> 00:06:48,942
There's a lot
of great marketers.

00:06:48,942 --> 00:06:50,677
What there aren't
are a lot of people

00:06:50,677 --> 00:06:52,512
who are great marketers
or branders

00:06:52,512 --> 00:06:53,713
who also know
how to monetize.

00:06:53,713 --> 00:06:55,615
That's what makes you
a great entrepreneur.

00:06:55,615 --> 00:06:58,318
You know, it's just not
a great investment.

00:06:58,318 --> 00:06:59,819
I mean, I would do anything

00:06:59,819 --> 00:07:01,988
to be in business with you
