for me to get excited.

00:07:07,928 --> 00:07:09,729
I think you'd be
an amazing partner.

00:07:09,729 --> 00:07:11,564
Is there a percentage that

00:07:11,564 --> 00:07:12,799
you would feel like you
had skin in the game

00:07:12,799 --> 00:07:14,634
