all of this stuff.
Greiner: Wow.

00:34:44,649 --> 00:34:47,652
She's, like, taking
her last breath.

00:34:47,652 --> 00:34:50,555
Well, the end of the story
is that she survived.

00:34:50,555 --> 00:34:51,723
I survived.
Yay!

00:34:51,723 --> 00:34:53,892
That was the motivation
to make this unit?

