00:35:06,304 --> 00:35:07,339
[ Laughter ]

00:35:07,339 --> 00:35:07,839
Tell her!
Tell her!

00:35:07,839 --> 00:35:09,541
First of all,
this is not a flashlight.

00:35:09,541 --> 00:35:11,810
This is a solar‐power,
rechargeable

00:35:11,810 --> 00:35:14,045
light and power device
that's used around the world

00:35:14,045 --> 00:35:16,681
in the most rugged conditions
you could possibly imagine.

00:35:16,681 --> 00:35:18,550
Otherwise known as
a flashlight.
No.

00:35:18,550 --> 00:35:20,085
No, it's rechargeable.
[ Laughs ]

00:35:20,085 --> 00:35:22,354
It's a light and power device
that will keep you safe

00:35:22,354 --> 00:35:22,988
and your
family safe.

00:35:22,988 --> 00:35:25,690
So it's the device formerly
