00:36:52,644 --> 00:36:54,713
$36,000.
Oy.

00:36:54,713 --> 00:36:57,882
When you started with
the NGOs in 30 countries,

00:36:57,882 --> 00:37:00,518
when you were selling to them,
not giving it to them,

00:37:00,518 --> 00:37:01,653
what were your sales then?

00:37:01,653 --> 00:37:03,688
About $30,000
for the whole year.

00:37:03,688 --> 00:37:05,824
For the whole year?
Yep. Yep.

00:37:05,824 --> 00:37:09,060
Is there anything
proprietary in this tech?

