We went on and bought every
single flashlight, lantern,

00:37:12,897 --> 00:37:15,667
cellphone charger,
solar panel out there

00:37:15,667 --> 00:37:16,935
and took them apart.

00:37:16,935 --> 00:37:19,604
And we took all of the bad stuff
and we threw it out,

00:37:19,604 --> 00:37:20,805
and we kept
the good stuff.

00:37:20,805 --> 00:37:22,040
But, Gene, I give you credit,

00:37:22,040 --> 00:37:23,708
you do better than anybody...
‐Hang on, Mark.

00:37:23,708 --> 00:37:26,444
...of talking around a question
and not answering it.

00:37:26,444 --> 00:37:27,846
You tell me
what the question is.

00:37:27,846 --> 00:37:29,748
Is there anything
proprietary?

