00:37:54,539 --> 00:37:55,907
Greiner: Is it
intellectual property?

00:37:55,907 --> 00:37:57,475
No, it's not.
Do you have a patent on it?

00:37:57,475 --> 00:37:58,676
I don't have
a patent on it.

00:37:58,676 --> 00:38:01,579
This product has merit,
good functionality.

