It's way too expensive.

00:38:03,014 --> 00:38:05,850
The way to make money with this
is to figure out a way

00:38:05,850 --> 00:38:08,620
to go direct‐to‐consumer,
online only.

00:38:08,620 --> 00:38:09,621
Forget retail.

00:38:09,621 --> 00:38:11,523
$29.95.

