I want you to do this ‐‐
I want you to say "Make money."

00:38:29,574 --> 00:38:31,543
Please say it.
Okay, "Make money."

00:38:31,543 --> 00:38:32,777
"Make money."
I'm out.

00:38:32,777 --> 00:38:34,913
Okay. Thank you
for your consideration.
Oh, okay.

00:38:34,913 --> 00:38:37,682
So, guys,
you've got a great product.
Thank you.

00:38:37,682 --> 00:38:40,018
But you've got to be able
to sell that product.
Yes.

00:38:40,018 --> 00:38:42,554
And you haven't been able
to demonstrate yet

