a path and a plan

00:38:47,091 --> 00:38:50,562
where you're going to be able
to blow these things out, right?

00:38:50,562 --> 00:38:52,730
So for those reasons,
I'm out.

00:38:52,730 --> 00:38:55,500
I'm in complete agreement.
I like the product.

00:38:55,500 --> 00:38:56,601
I think it's
a good product,

